From Agaju Madugba, Katsina The Vice Chancellor, Federal University Dutsin-Ma (FUDMA), Prof. Armaya’u Hamisu Bichi, has been appointed member, Governing Council, Maryam Abacha American University of Nigeria (MAAUN), Kano, Kano State. The President and Founder, MAAUN, Prof. Adamu Abubakar Gwarzo, while congratulating the appointee said the choice of Prof. Bichi followed a rigorous search among eminent personalities distinguished for their ingenuity and commitment to promoting education and human development. A statement by the FUDMA Public Relations Officer, Habibu Umar Aminu, quoted Gwarzo as explaining that, “your choice is informed by these qualities especially your exemplary scholarship.”